---
// Welcome.astro — Branded homepage for FERSmath
---

<!-- ─── Announcement Banner ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div
  style="background-color: var(--color-gold-400); padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem; text-align: center;"
>
  <p
    style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary-700);"
  >
    🎉 New: FERS High-3 Average Salary Calculator is live — <a
      href="/calculator/high-3"
      style="color: var(--color-primary-700); text-decoration: underline;"
      >Calculate your High-3 →</a
    >
  </p>
</div>

<!-- ─── Nav ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<header
  style="background-color: var(--color-primary-700); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-primary-600);"
>
  <div
    style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 4rem;"
  >
    <a
      href="/"
      style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none;"
    >
      <div
        style="width: 2rem; height: 2rem; background-color: var(--color-gold-400); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"
      >
        <svg
          width="18"
          height="18"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <path
            d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"
            stroke="#0F2244"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <span
        style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; letter-spacing: -0.025em;"
        >FERSmath</span
      >
    </a>
    <nav style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem;">
      <a
        href="/calculator/high-3"
        style="color: var(--color-primary-100); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none;"
        >Calculators</a
      >
      <a
        href="/blog"
        style="color: var(--color-primary-100); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none;"
        >Articles</a
      >
      <a
        href="/about"
        style="color: var(--color-primary-100); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none;"
        >About</a
      >
      <a
        href="/calculator/high-3"
        style="background-color: var(--color-gold-400); color: var(--color-primary-700); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none;"
        >Get Started</a
      >
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
<!-- ─── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section
  style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-700) 0%, var(--color-primary-600) 60%, var(--color-teal-600) 100%); padding: 6rem 1.5rem;"
>
  <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
    <span
      style="display: inline-block; background-color: rgba(201,160,53,0.15); color: var(--color-gold-300); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.375rem 1rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(201,160,53,0.3);"
    >
      Retirement Planning Made Clear
    </span>
    <h1
      style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); font-weight: 700; color: white; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin: 0 0 1.5rem;"
    >
      FERS Math<br />
      <span style="color: var(--color-gold-400);"
        >& Clarity</span
      >
    </h1>
    <p
      style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--color-primary-100); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;"
    >
      Sophisticated calculators and trusted financial insights to help you
      understand exactly where you stand — and what it takes to get where you
      want to be.
    </p>
    <div
      style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;"
    >
      <a
        href="/calculator/high-3"
        style="background-color: var(--color-gold-400); color: var(--color-primary-700); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.875rem 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);"
      >
        Calculate My High-3
      </a>
      <a
        href="/calculator/salary-lookup"
        style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white; font-weight: 500; font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.875rem 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);"
      >
        Salary Data
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── Calculators ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="background-color: var(--color-surface); padding: 5rem 1.5rem;">
  <div style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h2
        style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary-700); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;"
      >
        Retirement Calculators
      </h2>
      <p
        style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-muted); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto;"
      >
        Built for accuracy. Designed for clarity. Each tool models real-world
        retirement scenarios.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;"
    >
      <!-- High-3 Calculator — LIVE -->
      <a
        href="/calculator/high-3"
        style="background-color: var(--color-card); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold-400); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; text-decoration: none; display: block; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);"
      >
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
        >
          <span style="font-size: 1.75rem;">🏛️</span>
          <span
            style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); background-color: var(--color-gold-100); color: var(--color-gold-600);"
            >Live Now</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary-700); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; line-height: 1.3;"
        >
          High-3 Average Salary Calculator
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"
        >
          Calculate your FERS High-3 using OPM's 360-day rule. Enter your full
          GS grade and step history to find your highest 36-month window.
        </p>
        <div
          style="margin-top: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-teal-500); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;"
        >
          Open Calculator
          <svg
            width="14"
            height="14"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Salary History Lookup — LIVE -->
      <a
        href="/calculator/salary-lookup"
        style="background-color: var(--color-card); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold-400); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; text-decoration: none; display: block; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);"
      >
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
        >
          <span style="font-size: 1.75rem;">📊</span>
          <span
            style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); background-color: var(--color-gold-100); color: var(--color-gold-600);"
            >Live Now</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary-700); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; line-height: 1.3;"
        >
          GS Salary History Lookup
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"
        >
          Pick a grade, step, and locality area to see every year of
          available pay data and a chart of how the salary has grown.
        </p>
        <div
          style="margin-top: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-teal-500); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;"
        >
          Open Calculator
          <svg
            width="14"
            height="14"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Coming Soon cards -->
      <div
        style="background-color: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; display: block; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); opacity: 0.6;"
      >
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
        >
          <span style="font-size: 1.75rem;">📈</span>
          <span
            style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); background-color: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b;"
            >Coming Soon</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary-700); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; line-height: 1.3;"
        >
          TSP Projection Calculator
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"
        >
          Project your Thrift Savings Plan balance at retirement based on
          contributions, agency match, and fund selection.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        style="background-color: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; display: block; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); opacity: 0.6;"
      >
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
        >
          <span style="font-size: 1.75rem;">📅</span>
          <span
            style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); background-color: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b;"
            >Coming Soon</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary-700); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; line-height: 1.3;"
        >
          FERS Supplement Estimator
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"
        >
          Estimate your FERS Supplement — the bridge payment you receive before
          age 62 that approximates your Social Security benefit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        style="background-color: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; display: block; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); opacity: 0.6;"
      >
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
        >
          <span style="font-size: 1.75rem;">🏦</span>
          <span
            style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: var(--radius-full); background-color: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b;"
            >Coming Soon</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary-700); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; line-height: 1.3;"
        >
          FERS Basic Annuity Calculator
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"
        >
          Calculate your full FERS basic annuity including survivor benefit
          options and the impact of retiring before or after age 62.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── Articles ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section
  style="background-color: var(--color-primary-700); padding: 5rem 1.5rem;"
>
  <div style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h2
        style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;"
      >
        Latest Articles
      </h2>
      <p
        style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary-100); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto;"
      >
        Clear, unbiased financial writing — no ads, no sponsored content.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;"
    >
      <a
        href="/blog"
        style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; text-decoration: none; display: block;"
      >
        <span
          style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-gold-400);"
          >Strategy</span
        >
        <h3
          style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.35;"
        >
          The 4% Rule in 2025: Does It Still Hold Up?
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-primary-100); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 1.25rem;"
        >
          With elevated valuations and lower expected returns, we examine
          whether the classic safe withdrawal rate still protects retirees.
        </p>
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-primary-200);"
        >
          <span>Jul 8, 2025</span><span>8 min read</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/blog"
        style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; text-decoration: none; display: block;"
      >
        <span
          style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-gold-400);"
          >Tax Planning</span
        >
        <h3
          style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.35;"
        >
          Roth Conversion Ladders: A Step-by-Step Guide
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-primary-100); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 1.25rem;"
        >
          How to strategically convert traditional IRA funds to Roth over time
          to minimize lifetime taxes in retirement.
        </p>
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-primary-200);"
        >
          <span>Jul 2, 2025</span><span>12 min read</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/blog"
        style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; text-decoration: none; display: block;"
      >
        <span
          style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-gold-400);"
          >Social Security</span
        >
        <h3
          style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.35;"
        >
          Why Waiting Until 70 Is Almost Always Worth It
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-primary-100); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 1.25rem;"
        >
          The math behind delaying Social Security and why most retirees leave
          significant money on the table by claiming early.
        </p>
        <div
          style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-primary-200);"
        >
          <span>Jun 25, 2025</span><span>6 min read</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
      <a
        href="/blog"
        style="display: inline-block; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25); color: white; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none;"
      >
        View All Articles
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</main>

<!-- ─── Footer ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<footer
  style="background-color: var(--color-primary-800); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding: 3rem 1.5rem;"
>
  <div
    style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; text-align: center;"
  >
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
      <div
        style="width: 1.5rem; height: 1.5rem; background-color: var(--color-gold-400); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"
      >
        <svg
          width="12"
          height="12"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <path
            d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"
            stroke="#0F2244"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <span
        style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: white;"
        >FERSmath</span
      >
    </div>
    <p
      style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-primary-200); max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"
    >
      FERSmath provides educational tools and information for retirement
      planning purposes only. This is not financial advice. Always consult a
      qualified financial advisor before making investment decisions.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-primary-300); margin: 0;">
      &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} FERSmath. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
